Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.11,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\bord0\1c&H67646D&\pos(500,394)}別被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,包紮完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就算被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也絕不能說出實情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,絕不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是宇佐的同班同學對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,原來妳叫香織呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是二年四班的伊萬莉瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐真是很可愛對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是既開朗活潑 又為朋友著想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這傘給妳撐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我家就在附近而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,妳指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是去跟蹤伊萬莉同學了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是非常好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不是說過嗎 不能懷疑她那種人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們以後也要注意喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:55.33,BackGround,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 小瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說 我想買新的溜溜球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:05.42,BackGround,,0,0,0,,小瑞覺得哪種比較好？
